	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad me hisce diebus scripsit d. <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> in hęc verba: "In praesenti hoc abs te scire cupio, an gratum tibi futurum sit, si transferaris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l582" cert="high">Zofingam</placeName> in locum d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20907" cert="high">Ieorgii</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Die Berufung von <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20907" cert="high">Jörg Joachim</persName> nach <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1104" cert="high">Wynigen</placeName> wurde widerrufen; s. Pfister, Die Präd. d. bern. Aarg. S. 141f, Nr. 1115f (irrtüml. Joh. Georg Will; vgl. Nachtr. zu <bibl>HBBW</bibl> I-X).</note>; nam ille translatus est ad aliam quandam ecclesiam, et vacat illius locus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quamprimum fieri potest, significa michi animum tuum; neque enim causa ista moram ferre potest" etc.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Super hac <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculi</persName> petitione cupio ex animo sententiam tuam audire; hanc, quam primum potueris, michi significa, charissime frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praesentium lator in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniam</placeName> proficiscitur, pernoctavit apud me; videtur michi valde doctus esse et rerum Christi cupidissimus; tu illum suscipe pro tua in peregrinos charitate.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, amice incomparabilis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Date <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l285" cert="high">Lentzburgi</placeName> 16. septembris 1553.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8440" cert="high">Gervasius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fideli Christi servo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heynricho Bullingero</persName>, amico veteri et fratri in Christo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
